results.name: Inverse of sequence A052330 considered as a permutation of the natural numbers.
comment: A052330 is not exactly a permutation because it has offset 0 but doesn't contain 0. A052331 is its exact inverse, which has offset 1 and contains 0. - _David Wasserman_, Feb 24 2005
results.author: _Howard A. Landman_, Sep 25 2001
